Package: zotapir
Type: Package
Title: Synchronized Zotero Bibliography in R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Patrice Godard
Maintainer: Patrice Godard <patrice.godard@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides a way to maintain a synchronized version
of Zotero (http://zotero.org) bibliography.
Depends:
   httr,
   tibble,
   dplyr,
   magrittr,
Imports:
   glue
